{"type":"answer","id":84906,"parentType":"question","parentId":11691,"uid":16872,"contents":"好像有人問過了。<br>\n<br>\n我是真心看不出民主和槍械管制有甚麼直接關係，如果政治制度好、法治優良，根本有沒有都不成問題，反倒說很多民主國家的公民都不能帶槍，像日本這種公民素養高但自殺率高生活壓抑的也不適合持槍。<br>\n<br>\n先看持槍合法性<br>\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Overview_of_gun_laws_by_nation\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Overview_of_gun_laws_by_nation</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/90/Gun_laws.svg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/90/Gun_laws.svg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/90/Gun_laws.svg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n紅色全禁，藍色無管制，其他自己想像<br>\n<br>\n再看因槍械死亡的統計，每十萬人口計：<br>\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_firearm-related_death_rate\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_firearm-related_death_rate</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/biPChTO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/biPChTO.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/biPChTO.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n值得注意的是，頭十名都有九名都是美洲國家，第十名就是美國了。<br>\n<br>\n接下來看犯罪率：<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/crime-rate-by-country/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/crime-rate-by-country/</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/qatar-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Qatar</a>&nbsp;12 2,832,067<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/united-arab-emirates-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">United Arab Emirates</a>&nbsp;15.52&nbsp;9,770,529<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/japan-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Japan</a>&nbsp;15.91&nbsp;126,860,301<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/taiwan-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Taiwan</a>&nbsp;16.22&nbsp;23,773,876<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/hong-kong-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Hong Kong</a>&nbsp;18.1 7,436,154<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/georgia-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Georgia</a>&nbsp;20.18 3,996,765<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/armenia-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Armenia</a>&nbsp;20.78 2,957,731<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/switzerland-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Switzerland</a>&nbsp;21.18 8,591,365<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/oman-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Oman</a>&nbsp;21.55&nbsp;4,974,986<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/slovenia-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Slovenia</a>&nbsp;22.01 2,078,654<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/estonia-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Estonia</a>&nbsp;22.17 1,325,648<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/finland-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Finland</a>&nbsp;22.75 5,532,156<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/iceland-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Iceland</a>&nbsp;23.15 339,031<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/austria-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Austria</a>&nbsp;23.23 8,955,102<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/croatia-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Croatia</a>&nbsp;24.23 4,130,304<br>\n<a href=\"http://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/denmark-population/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Denmark</a>&nbsp;24.72 5,771,876<br>\n<br>\n可以看出，一般公民持槍對治安並沒有絕對正比作用，那些犯罪率低而能合法持槍的國家，對槍械管制也有相當的嚴格程度，如瑞士和北歐國家，這些都是公民教育領先至少三十年的國家。僅供參考。","date":"2019-11-22","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":1}